{"tid":1321253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到班垃圾見到] 由孫子兵法睇沙田攻略","createTime":"2019-07-15T15:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T15:40:34.000Z","uid":273012,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"56f56abe5ce3c5bf526390f1f843636de13379b7","tid":1321253,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"尋日一連串嘅清場 可見警隊嘅commander有幾垃圾 犯哂兵家最常見嘅錯誤 <br />\n以下只係一啲節錄。<br />\n強調大家研究中國文化，真係博大精深，歷久常新架。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>謀攻第三</strong></span><br />\n故用兵之法，十則圍之，五則攻之，倍則分之，敵則能戰之，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">少則能逃之，不若則能避之。</span></span></strong>故小敵之堅，大敵之擒也。<br />\n<br />\n若決定伐兵，則在用兵的策略上需考量敵我的兵力差距。當我軍兵力是敵軍的十倍時，可打包圍戰逼對方投降。若是五倍，便可進攻。若只有兩倍，優勢不夠大，最好能將敵軍的兵力分散，提高每一戰的相對優勢並逐一擊破。若勢均力敵，則需要有好的奇謀策略提高勝率。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">若兵力比敵軍少，則不出戰，設法逃躲。要是整體不如對方，就要懂得認輸，儘速逃離，不要無謂的堅持不跑，</span></span></strong>學會放棄當下，未來才有機會再起。<br />\n<br />\n諗一諗，尋日警察咁嘅人數，佢地入黎除左比人打，仲想做到啲咩。<br />\n我如果係啲警察，今次真係屌七哂上面所有嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址： <a href=\"https://medium.com/sheracaolity/%E5%AD%AB%E5%AD%90%E5%85%B5%E6%B3%95-%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80-1ec6ec9984c7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fsheracaolity%2F%25E5%25AD%25AB%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%2585%25B5%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25AE%2580-1ec6ec9984c7&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=83e5744b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/sheracaolity/%E5%AD%AB%E5%AD%90%E5%85%B5%E6%B3%95-%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80-1ec6ec9984c7</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>軍爭第七</strong></span><br />\n故用兵之法，高陵勿向，背丘勿逆，佯北勿從，銳卒勿攻，餌兵勿食，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歸師勿遏，圍師必闕，窮寇勿迫</span></span></strong>，此用兵之法也。<br />\n<br />\n所以，用兵的原則是：對占據高地、背倚丘陵之敵，不要作正面仰攻；對於假裝敗逃之敵，不要跟踪追擊；敵人的精銳部隊不要強攻；敵人的誘餌之兵，不要貪食；<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對正在向本土撤退的部隊不要去阻截；對被包圍的敵軍，要預留缺口；對於陷入絕境的敵人，不要過分逼迫</span></span></strong>，這些都是用兵的基本原則。<br />\n<br />\n尋日係犯哂所有錯誤，先會迫到人變成絕地嘅死士。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_71e461e90102z81s.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.sina.com.cn%2Fs%2Fblog_71e461e90102z81s.html&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=06bdee66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_71e461e90102z81s.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">行軍第九</span></strong><br />\n凡軍好高而惡下，貴陽而賤陰，養生而處實，軍無百疾，是謂必勝。<br />\n凡地有絕澗、<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天井</span></span></strong>、天牢、天羅、天陷、<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天隙</span></span></strong>，必亟去之，勿近也。<br />\n<br />\n天井：四周是高岩山石，中央低洼<br />\n天隙：山間狹谷<br />\n<br />\n有冇留意同琴日嘅地形何其相似。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新城市天井</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n沙田商埸出面就係天隙</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢啲係中埋伏嘅極佳地點，你走入去，只可以話你冇腦。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">地形第十</span></strong><br />\n故兵有走者、有弛者、有陷者、有崩者、有亂者、有北者。凡此六者，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非天之災，將之過也</span></span></strong>。<br />\n將不能料敵，以少合衆，以弱擊強，兵無選鋒，曰北。<br />\n<br />\n而《地形篇》中，孫子給出了六種因為將領失責導致必敗的情況作為警惕：<br />\n走：雙方條件相當，但用自己十分之一的兵力去和敵軍作戰，以一敵十，自不量力。<br />\n弛：兵士強悍，但將領懦弱、指揮不動，導致紀律鬆弛。<br />\n陷：將領很強，但士卒跟不上，沒有被訓練好。<br />\n崩：小將對大將不服，遇敵時擅自率隊出戰，大將沒辦法有效指揮、執行大戰略。<br />\n亂：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">將領管理無章法，出兵列陣縱橫不整、橫衝直撞。</span></strong><br />\n北：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">將領不能判斷敵情，以少擊多、以弱擊強，用兵不懂得選精銳當先鋒隊</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">將之過也，即係個警司垃圾。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n九變第八<br />\n孫子曰：凡用兵之法，將受命於君，合軍聚眾。圮地無舍，衢地合交，絕地無留，圍地則謀，死地則戰。途有所不由，軍有所不擊，城有所不攻，地有所不爭，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">*******君命有所不受*******</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果個一哥咁垃圾，明知送你去死你都要去，有樣野叫做「君命有所不受」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"9de2bd6342de1f9ac4151cc769e0e673bb43eb0d","tid":1321253,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:23:51.000Z","msg":"推到班垃圾見到"},{"pid":"682f97009996093dd55140d343f51ea8fc7ae261","tid":1321253,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:24:03.000Z","msg":"推到班垃圾見到"},{"pid":"fd42f43cf2135ca879e2c234a43f959a01398b8c","tid":1321253,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:24:23.000Z","msg":"推到班垃圾見到"},{"pid":"04f2e0e886891308240535f9fe06a23f138971de","tid":1321253,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:25:08.000Z","msg":"推到班垃圾見到"},{"pid":"8322f2fb67eeff0f0fa8a3d0b60f6c6409c1bd92","tid":1321253,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:25:51.000Z","msg":"推到班垃圾見到"},{"pid":"81be8d01a4dbea113deb507c97aace2c9674cb68","tid":1321253,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:26:30.000Z","msg":"推到班垃圾見到"},{"pid":"667dc3b267c0fcf10e6be895d15d8fb820b361a1","tid":1321253,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:27:25.000Z","msg":"推到班垃圾見到"},{"pid":"e99e03657eb26c7efe64e153e4998c4ccb414239","tid":1321253,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"推到班垃圾見到"},{"pid":"2c2e76ea52bc8815daaa0a9a0b2857ba592173e6","tid":1321253,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:31:12.000Z","msg":"推到班垃圾見到"},{"pid":"46c6d60107a6fe6f662781b06eea19ffb43dc699","tid":1321253,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:32:52.000Z","msg":"推到班垃圾見到"},{"pid":"edfd059bbb3c1516722139649345df738e7c7c52","tid":1321253,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:35:27.000Z","msg":"如果警察聽孫子話 一早有民心<br />\n孫子第一篇就教你有國先有家 <br />\n有家先有兵 軍隊要有人民支持 <br />\n根本就係教你做人腳踏實地 唔好取巧"},{"pid":"43ddd52ab6c9f184904b614e8b4fe6a28618d5c0","tid":1321253,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edfd059bbb3c1516722139649345df738e7c7c52","tid":1321253,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:35:27.000Z","msg":"如果警察聽孫子話 一早有民心<br />\n孫子第一篇就教你有國先有家 <br />\n有家先有兵 軍隊要有人民支持 <br />\n根本就係教你做人腳踏實地 唔好取巧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"道者，令民與上同意，可與之死，可與之生，而不畏危也。"}]}